### Health check
GET http://localhost:17000/health
Accept: application/json

### List all concerts
GET http://localhost:17000/concerts
Accept: application/json

### List concerts with title filter
GET http://localhost:17000/concerts?title=Christmas&limit=100
Accept: application/json

### List concerts with location filter
GET http://localhost:17000/concerts?genre=Rock&location=New York&limit=10
Accept: application/json

### List concerts with genre filter
GET http://localhost:17000/concerts?genre=Rock&limit=100
Accept: application/json

### List concerts with pagination
GET http://localhost:17000/concerts?limit=5&offset=0
Accept: application/json

### Get concert by ID
GET http://localhost:17000/concerts/146
Accept: application/json

### Sync concerts from Ticketmaster - default (US, today, 20 results)
GET http://localhost:17000/concerts/sync
Accept: application/json

### Sync concerts from Ticketmaster - GB only
GET http://localhost:17000/concerts/sync?country=GB
Accept: application/json

### Sync concerts from Ticketmaster - specific date
GET http://localhost:17000/concerts/sync?country=US&date=2025-12-30
Accept: application/json

### Sync concerts from Ticketmaster - custom size
GET http://localhost:17000/concerts/sync?country=US&size=50
Accept: application/json

### Sync concerts from Ticketmaster - all filters
GET http://localhost:17000/concerts/sync?country=US&date=2025-12-20&size=30
Accept: application/json

